description:
In a desperate final battle against Queen Chrysalis, Cadence must overcome her heartbreak and reignite the power of love before the world succumbs to darkness forever. 
Will her shattered heart doom Equestria, or can she prove that loves light can outshine even the deepest despair?
https://www.patreon.com/c/Tamers12345
https://x.com/TheTamers12345
Thanks to https://x.com/rakuda_ch for letting me use this beautiful rendition of This Day Aria! https://youtu.be/Rp6yqNG60_0
